PrecisTransfer to the Province of BRITISH COLUMBIA, for a term of five (5) years, of the administration and control over some 1,664.4 square metres of land situate at DEASE LAKE AIRPORT, which are to be used for the operation and maintenance of a lightning detector and other electrical and communications lines required in connection therewith.
